WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.350
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:03.390
Day

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:06.749
63. I took two days to get

00:00:06.759 --> 00:00:09.070
direction because I'm asking the

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:10.589
Lord, 'What do you have

00:00:10.599 --> 00:00:12.230
for your people? What do we need to

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:16.349
be praying about?'Little

00:00:16.349 --> 00:00:16.359
pulses are

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:19.550
just what's coming

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:22.710
up to me: praying over the

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:26.790
terrorist attacks, praying over what

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.950
the Lord showed me. I'm going to

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.749
go over some of these things the Lord

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:33.869
has shown me about terrorist attacks

00:00:33.879 --> 00:00:36.430
because a lot of you are new here

00:00:36.430 --> 00:00:36.440
and

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:38.389
have not watched those old

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:39.790
videos. I know because they haven't

00:00:39.790 --> 00:00:39.800
gone

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.830
up in view count, and there's

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:44.350
hundreds of thousands of you now versus

00:00:44.350 --> 00:00:44.360
when

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:46.709
the Lord told me this stuff

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:49.750
back when I only had 30,000 people.

00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:51.389
I'm going to go over them again, and you

00:00:51.399 --> 00:00:55.910
need to know. Last

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:59.029
time I gave you the word for

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:00.470
the remnant,

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.869
for the presents that is coming.

00:01:02.879 --> 00:01:06.550
I've been on a real steady path of

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:09.590
encouragement and not getting down. The

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.469
warnings that I get in my spirit

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:16.030
on a daily basis... I'm trying to be

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:18.149
encouraging during the holiday

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:21.510
season and telling you all hope, which is

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:24.830
truth. I'm not here to give you honey; I'm

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:27.710
here to tell the remnant

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:30.710
there's good days ahead for you,

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:33.990
but there is also a devil out there, and

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.030
there's a plan of the enemy to kill,

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:39.109
steal, and destroy. So I have to give

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:42.230
you both sides of the coin. This side

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:45.109
will have the potential to scare you if you're not

00:01:45.119 --> 00:01:47.149
rooted and grounded in love, because

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:49.910
perfect love casts out all fear.

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:55.230
This is

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:57.190
the part that is hard to give because

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:59.350
there's a lot of people that go, 'Oh, the

00:01:59.350 --> 00:01:59.360
sky's

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:01.990
falling, Chicken Little,'and I say no, the

00:02:01.990 --> 00:02:02.000
sky's

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.190
not falling, but the Lord

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:06.230
always tells you in advance what the

00:02:06.240 --> 00:02:08.790
enemy's trying to plot and scheme.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:13.229
His job is to destroy and

00:02:13.239 --> 00:02:16.070
to wipe out lots of people, but the Bible

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:18.589
says that we have power and authority

00:02:18.599 --> 00:02:20.589
over the devil. So I'm going to put that

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:22.830
out there first before I tell you about

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:25.110
what I have seen coming again. The

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:28.190
Lord is warning me that this is a plan that is

00:02:28.190 --> 00:02:28.200
afoot;

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:31.030
this is what

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:32.949
they're going to try to do in the days

00:02:32.959 --> 00:02:35.150
ahead. This is not something that we have

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:37.509
averted yet, but this is something that

00:02:37.519 --> 00:02:39.309
the enemy is going to try to do in the

00:02:39.319 --> 00:02:43.550
near future. So we as the body have

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.910
our antennas up. We're watching on the

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:48.030
wall. I had a really cool email from

00:02:48.040 --> 00:02:50.390
a guy whose son prays in the

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.910
spirit with us as he plays his violin,

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:56.270
and I encouraged him. Oh my goodness, he's 17

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:59.390
years old,

00:02:59.390 --> 00:02:59.400
and

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:01.030
praying in the spirit and

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:03.110
playing his instrument. I'm telling

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.270
you, the Lord's going to use this young

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:07.509
man to do mighty things for Him with

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:09.550
that instrument.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:11.670
You start praying in the spirit,

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:12.789
and the Holy Spirit's going to start

00:03:12.799 --> 00:03:14.750
flowing through that instrument,

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:15.869
and you're going to see people getting

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:17.509
healed whenever you start playing,

00:03:17.519 --> 00:03:19.630
just like David played

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:23.270
for Saul and caused the demons to go.

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:27.430
Worship causes demons to flee. So as you

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:29.830
worship on that violin and you start

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.910
playing, play with the Holy Spirit, young

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.949
man. I

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:36.229
believe with all my heart that God's

00:03:36.239 --> 00:03:38.670
going to use you in a mighty way in

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:40.910
these last days with this younger

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:43.110
generation. It's exciting about your

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:44.630
dad and you praying in the car on the

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:46.869
way to school. I'm excited about that,

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.470
glory to God! That's what we're here for:

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:50.990
to teach

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:54.390
you how to stand as watchmen on the wall,

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:58.270
so that you'll

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:00.229
do it for yourself.

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:01.630
This isn't a

00:04:01.640 --> 00:04:03.630
Brandon show, a Diana show,

00:04:03.630 --> 00:04:03.640
or

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.589
a Braden show; this is a Jesus

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:08.550
show. He's on here to tell you

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:11.869
through me that you have what it takes.

00:04:11.879 --> 00:04:13.750
That same power in the Holy Spirit

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.429
that dwells on the inside of me dwells

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:17.789
on the inside of you, and every

00:04:17.799 --> 00:04:20.550
single one of you has the ability to

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:23.469
call down fire. Every single one of you

00:04:23.469 --> 00:04:23.479
has

00:04:23.479 --> 00:04:25.710
the ability to tread on serpents

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.710
and scorpions, and nothing shall by any

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:30.909
means hurt you. Cling to and

00:04:30.919 --> 00:04:33.029
quote Psalm 91 and

00:04:33.039 --> 00:04:34.310
Psalm

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:37.110
23. In these last days we will see

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:39.629
dark, dark days, but the

00:04:39.639 --> 00:04:43.510
light has come on you. That all being

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:45.430
said, let me tell you what I saw and

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.469
what the Lord has warned me again

00:04:47.479 --> 00:04:48.909
that's

00:04:48.919 --> 00:04:53.230
coming. The Lord showed me three

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:58.230
men crossing the border in Arizona,

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:01.590
and these men, He said, were Al-Qaeda.

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:04.270
They are very high-ranking in the

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:06.469
Al-Qaeda organization.

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:10.310
The Lord showed me

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:13.670
these three men crossing the border

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:15.670
secretly. It looked like

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:19.070
mountains in the horizon,

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:22.029
deserty,

00:05:24.199 --> 00:05:25.790
and it was barely

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:28.830
daybreak

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:31.270
when they crossed over. They had

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:33.950
people waiting for them on the other

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:37.029
side to take them in what

00:05:37.029 --> 00:05:37.039
looked

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:39.870
like a black van, and they drove

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:41.909
them away out of the desert and

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:44.830
escaped. The Lord told me that they

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:48.309
are plotting and planning attacks in

00:05:48.319 --> 00:05:52.550
America as we speak. These men, and

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:55.790
there are literally thousands of them

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:58.469
that have crossed over the border over

00:05:58.479 --> 00:06:02.350
the course of the last four years during

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.870
Sleepy Joe's administration, and the Lord

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:09.710
told me that these men will

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:14.870
come up. When the time's been told

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:16.270
for them to do whatever they're going to

00:06:16.280 --> 00:06:18.070
do, they're going to come up out of the

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:19.230
ground like

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:21.670
ants. They're

00:06:21.670 --> 00:06:21.680
underground,

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:24.909
hidden somehow, and

00:06:24.919 --> 00:06:27.629
when it's time, I saw them coming up like

00:06:27.639 --> 00:06:30.990
red ants out of an anthill, and they

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.110
were going to do their attacks. It

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:36.390
was simultaneously more than one place

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:38.710
at one time—a bunch of

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:40.870
coordinated things happening to bring

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:44.469
fear and make people afraid to go and

00:06:44.479 --> 00:06:47.189
live life, because you don't

00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:49.029
know when it's going to happen next. But

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:51.830
these people had ill intentions to do

00:06:51.830 --> 00:06:51.840
mass

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:55.550
casualties, more than 9/11. I saw

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:57.909
them coming up out of the dens. These

00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:00.430
are different visions

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:04.670
from

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:07.869
different days, but they all go

00:07:07.869 --> 00:07:07.879
together

00:07:07.879 --> 00:07:11.189
like a puzzle. Then the Lord

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:13.589
showed

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:16.629
me them coming across the border, and

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:21.189
then I saw men with vials in their hands

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:23.589
that had

00:07:23.599 --> 00:07:26.869
biological stuff inside of these

00:07:26.879 --> 00:07:30.070
test tubes.

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.629
I know they weren't wearing

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:35.790
these garments for real, but the

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:39.550
Lord was showing me they were in white

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:42.189
turban hats and white outfits. The

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:43.629
Lord said they are

00:07:43.639 --> 00:07:47.790
Al-Qaeda again. I saw them at

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:49.390
water

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:53.830
facilities, treatment plants, and lakes.

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:56.869
They took

00:07:56.879 --> 00:08:00.110
a metal spoon,

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:03.350
and I saw them dumping the

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:06.550
stuff with rubber gloves on.

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:10.589
Just a little bit in a lake,

00:08:10.599 --> 00:08:14.070
if it was the city's supply

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:17.350
and source of drinking water, would not be

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:21.830
detected in the facilities to filter

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:25.589
it. So I saw them pouring this

00:08:25.599 --> 00:08:28.070
stuff into lake reservoirs and into

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:30.149
our streams. I don't know what it

00:08:30.159 --> 00:08:34.469
is, but it affected all the water

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:37.589
supply.

00:08:37.599 --> 00:08:40.909
This

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:43.630
was all down in the

00:08:43.640 --> 00:08:49.190
Florida Panhandle area. I saw Georgia,

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:52.190
Mississippi, Alabama, and the Florida

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:56.030
Panhandle all lit up in the spirit

00:08:56.030 --> 00:08:56.040
realm—the

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:58.269
bottom half toward the Gulf Coast.

00:08:58.279 --> 00:09:00.190
This affected clear down through

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:03.670
New Orleans and Houston on

00:09:03.680 --> 00:09:06.230
the coast because they couldn't figure

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:09.590
out which water was tainted and which water was not

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.910
when this event would

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:15.750
take place. I saw

00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:18.790
literally

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:22.030
hundreds of thousands

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:25.910
of people

00:09:25.910 --> 00:09:25.920
who

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:28.910
had drunk the water and

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:30.670
did not know that they were

00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:33.269
poisoned. I saw children, because they

00:09:33.279 --> 00:09:36.350
were smaller, get sick first; they started

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:39.069
bending over and died right there.

00:09:39.079 --> 00:09:40.949
Then the mothers were trying to comfort

00:09:40.959 --> 00:09:42.710
their children and they were weeping, and

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:45.430
they passed on. The fathers passed on.

00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:47.790
Everybody in the family—it showed me it

00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:49.750
affected the weight of

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:52.750
the person, so

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:55.630
the less you weighed, the more

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:58.110
it

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:01.350
affected

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:03.269
you.

00:10:03.279 --> 00:10:04.470
That's just the way it showed,

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:08.069
I'm just assuming,

00:10:08.079 --> 00:10:10.630
I don't want to add to or take away

00:10:10.640 --> 00:10:12.470
from the vision.

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:22.030
I saw all these people

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:23.949
drinking it, and there

00:10:23.949 --> 00:10:23.959
were

00:10:23.959 --> 00:10:28.069
literally thousands of people

00:10:28.069 --> 00:10:28.079
perishing.

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:30.870
Houston was not

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:33.949
affected; Houston's water plants

00:10:33.959 --> 00:10:36.949
made all the people drink

00:10:36.949 --> 00:10:36.959
bottled

00:10:36.959 --> 00:10:39.949
water, but there was not enough

00:10:39.949 --> 00:10:39.959
bottled

00:10:39.959 --> 00:10:42.470
water from Houston all the way

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:45.269
across to Atlanta because there are so

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:47.470
many people in those areas.

00:10:49.839 --> 00:10:52.790
People were so

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:56.990
scared to drink the water. Unless you had

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:59.829
a water well,

00:10:59.839 --> 00:11:03.310
people in the major cities died from

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:06.389
lack of water because they could not get out.

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:07.990
There

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.949
wasn't enough water to

00:11:09.959 --> 00:11:12.150
service all the people, so

00:11:12.150 --> 00:11:12.160
they

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:13.790
were perishing from

00:11:13.800 --> 00:11:16.310
dehydration.

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:20.629
All the people who

00:11:20.639 --> 00:11:25.150
passed away had to be put in

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:29.910
bags. I saw mass graves the

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:34.590
size of football fields—humongous holes

00:11:34.600 --> 00:11:38.670
dug with them lining the bodies up

00:11:38.680 --> 00:11:41.110
because there weren't enough funeral

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:45.030
homes or enough

00:11:45.030 --> 00:11:45.040
way

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.150
to freeze the bodies.

00:11:51.079 --> 00:11:54.990
By government order, they put all

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:58.710
of these bodies inside of a massive hole.

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:00.670
I know this is alarming,

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:02.110
but I'm just warning you what I've

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:06.710
seen. They put a

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:11.389
massive, humongous eagle statue with its

00:12:11.399 --> 00:12:13.910
wings spread out

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:16.949
on a

00:12:16.959 --> 00:12:19.509
granite

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:22.629
monument,

00:12:22.639 --> 00:12:24.790
giving them

00:12:24.790 --> 00:12:24.800
true

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:27.389
honor and tribute to the

00:12:27.399 --> 00:12:30.430
fallen.

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:32.269
I

00:12:32.279 --> 00:12:34.550
saw the United States and all the writing on

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:37.389
it in this

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:40.350
one place where all the bodies were.

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:42.110
It was a massive

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:45.430
field. The people in these other

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:47.710
cities did not have enough water unless

00:12:47.710 --> 00:12:47.720
they

00:12:47.720 --> 00:12:50.230
had a well. People who

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.030
had a water well had lines of people

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:54.030
they were trying to help,

00:12:56.920 --> 00:12:58.389
but it still was not enough. We're

00:12:58.399 --> 00:13:02.550
talking millions of people from Houston

00:13:02.550 --> 00:13:02.560
and

00:13:02.560 --> 00:13:04.910
New Orleans all the way to Atlanta and

00:13:04.920 --> 00:13:08.150
Tallahassee. This

00:13:08.150 --> 00:13:08.160
event

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:11.750
was very serious.

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:14.550
I've seen this happening

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:17.030
with terrorist activity, so I'm going

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:18.470
to go over the terrorist things

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:20.590
I've seen.

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:24.470
I was shown a

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:28.550
massive barge coming

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:33.590
from what looked like Africa. These

00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:36.829
terrorists took over the

00:13:36.839 --> 00:13:40.509
boat, and nobody knew. They

00:13:40.509 --> 00:13:40.519
hijacked the

00:13:40.519 --> 00:13:42.550
boat

00:13:42.560 --> 00:13:45.790
and

00:13:45.800 --> 00:13:49.990
eliminated all the

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:54.550
crew. They had a

00:13:54.560 --> 00:13:58.629
briefcase device in the belly of this

00:13:58.639 --> 00:14:00.430
boat

